<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV25">
<l>eṅkōl vaḷaimuta lākkaṇṇaṉ maṇṇumviṇ ṇumaḷikkuñ</l>
<l>ceṅkōl vaḷaivu viḷaivikku māltiṟaṟ cēramarar</l>
<l>taṅkō ṉuṭaiyataṅ kōṉumpa rellā yavarkkuntaṅkō</l>
<l>ṉaṅkō ṉukakkun tuḻāyeṉcey yātiṉi nāṉilattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The reason being our beautiful bangles, under the just rule Kaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>provides for earth and heaven it reapes crookedness indeed,</l>
<l>the Tulsi that delights our king, the king of those in the light beyond, the king of the king</l>
<l>of the powerful immortals. What will it not do now in the four grounds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
